etical and practical interest. For example, it is shown\nthat, in a NOMA-enabled VLC system, the maximum rate at which information can\nbe transmitted over a static VLC communication channel with ambient light\nasymptotically converges to the Shannon Hartley capacity formula.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 17:26:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-18"}
