ts moving in the same\ndirection. In the high-magnetisation case, the accelerated particles form a\nbroken power-law energy distribution with a soft tail produced by particles\naccelerated in the minijets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 19:01:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 12:50:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-15"}
