 to disentangle the\nexistence and nature of an extended electroweak symmetry breaking sector\nvisible in $VV$ fusion: two-Higgs production, vector resonances, $\\gamma\\gamma$\nphysics and top-antitop production.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Nov 2019 19:29:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
